The applicable provisions state in pertinent part:
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Section 19\u8211\'3f117. Non-conforming buildings or structures.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
An existing non-conforming building or structure may be maintained and repaired, but shall not be structurally altered or added on to further the non-conformance; however, an existing non-conforming building or structure may be added onto or altered provided such addition, alteration or use is in compliance with this ordinance.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Section 19\u8211\'3f118. Non-conforming use of buildings and structures.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(a) The use of any building or structure not in conformance with this ordinance pertaining to uses permitted on the effective date of Ordinance No. 1\u8211\'3f1973 may not be:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
(3) Extended, enlarged or expanded.
\par 
}
}
}
}
}
